{"tid":814221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九龍站外 巴士撞翻私家車夾住途人","createTime":"2018-09-11T05:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T13:04:15.000Z","uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"177a614a711e4d2223fe3bd191c08a732148a93c","tid":814221,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"一輛雙層巴士，駛至西九龍站與柯士甸站之間路面，巴士車長突然不適，失控剷上行人路，撞傷一名途人，將他夾在欄杆之間，同時亦撞翻前面一輛私家車。巴士車長、途人及私家車司機乘客共4人受傷。大批警員、消防員及救護員出動拯救，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180911&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58667807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180911%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58667807&d=xqIHLRNbahW4qstUf4jHUMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d4aa6035\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180911%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58667807&h=dedccfa7\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180911&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58667807</a>"},{"pid":"6ad1ae1a737c0e6c7d79ba50d85fde736d8a8d0f","tid":814221,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6688bac6a996629f30da7a7cab934b25567103a","tid":814221,"uid":19287,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"這是配合高鐵通車的交通意外演習。廣深港高鐵於本月23日通車，除了鐵路運輸外，警方亦留意路面交通情況。今日特別進行交通意外演習，模擬西九龍站外發生車禍，讓各部門配合及應變。「車禍」中，警方、消防及救護員等出動近百人，場面迫真。"},{"pid":"ebcc0f51876aaae5ea7c80bb05ac8b6444e38901","tid":814221,"uid":50526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:02:03.000Z","msg":"氣氛緊張<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/do